No. 09-247 (R46-024). Ohio Valley Environmental Coalition, et al., Petitioners v. United States Army Corps of Engineers, et al. 561 U.S. 1051, 131 S. Ct. 51,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1141,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5682. August 19, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 556 F.3d 177.
